17	// RBTDRK — gauntlet canonical-establish fixture (§2 of release qualification)
18	//
19	// Establishes long-lived canonical state the gauntlet's downstream fixtures
20	// inherit:
21	//   1. depot_levy        — install canonical RBRR prefixes; levy a fresh canest depot
22	//   2. governor_mantle   — mantle governor against the canonical depot
23	//   3. retriever_invest  — invest a canonical retriever SA + access-probe
24	//   4. director_invest   — invest a canonical director SA + access-probe
25	//
26	// Disposition: StateProgressing. Each case carries a precondition probe via
27	// rbtdrb_Probe so a-la-carte single-case rerun fails cleanly when an earlier
28	// case's state is absent. Tabtarget invocations are responsible for waiting
29	// out their own propagation (no separate iam-propagation-wait case).
